The popup menu is made up of two parts. (1) background (2) menu item list

The scroll bar is made up of four parts. (1) up / left arrow buttons (2) down / right arrow buttons (3) bar background (4) the grip button Up and down / left and right arrow buttons on the mobile device is not necessary.
The slide bar is made up of three parts. (1) background (2) the expansion part (3) grip button
